Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.56,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我在大和之心中漸漸甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:42.70,Fumikiri_hmz1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H29272D&\fs79.999\fad(912,825)\pos(1413.333,891.334)}第{\c&H1EC1F0&\1a&H0A&}七{\c&H29272D&}話 {\c&H1EC1F0&\1a&H0A&}道{\c&H29272D&}口{\c&H1EC1F0&\1a&H0A&}的{\c&H29272D&}詩{\c&H1EC1F0&\1a&H0A&}人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.91,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在道口等車的這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.75,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總會洋溢出寫詩的激情的我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.25,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天跳動著5-7-5的節拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.33,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我將心中所想原原本本地寫在俳句本上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.65,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我就是道口的詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:53.71,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口的俳人是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:53.71,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}註：俳人，即寫俳句的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:55.56,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:57.68,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:00:59.36,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊道口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:00.44,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:05.29,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉 太深沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.07,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不刻意地歌頌愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:09.02,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只是反覆詠「道口」一詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:11.50,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就能感受到作者的深意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:15.13,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.04,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.23,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有所思量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.42,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,無意間連吐槽都成了5-7-5的調子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:26.22,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要為自己滲入基因的大和之心所拜服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.57,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然準確來說並不是5-7-5調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.22,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,中間7的部分額外多了一個音節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.17,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四捨五入就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.58,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 四捨五入就進位了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.90,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,進位變成 10-10-10調！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.88,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,10-10-10 多麼新穎的調子！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.39,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三重十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.00,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不…「三重十字俳句」！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.40,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,俳句間流露著中二般的帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.82,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是「三重十字俳句」流行起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.46,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定會被無數人所崇拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.27,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜我為師…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:57.95,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.99,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃邪王之眼的持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別西卜的使徒是也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}註：別西卜，基督教聖經中的鬼王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.71,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜服我吧 人類們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.09,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,缺乏知性…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:10.91,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四捨五入後覺得缺少一點感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.88,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪三重十字架引發了我的中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.60,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 必須封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.11,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,邪道不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.88,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必須寫些規矩的俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.39,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.83,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 怎樣以道口為題寫成俳句呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.04,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒聽說過描寫道口的俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.33,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且季語是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:31.57,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40.001}註：季語，俳句中規定表示季節的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:31.57,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「道口」是季語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.40,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.31,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必須在「道口」上加個別的什麼季語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.14,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才能組成俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.55,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.17,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:46.99,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雪花堆積
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.20,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,電車來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.55,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有感覺 很有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.27,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有積雪電車可能會停運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.02,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 道口…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.67,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一點詩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.77,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是寫愛情 歌頌愛情的詩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.93,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有寫入愛情 才稱得上是年輕人的詩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:06.52,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.39,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.58,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,用這三個詞組句
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.53,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.96,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,道口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.28,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,電車來 愛情不會走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.62,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪花慢慢飄落之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:20.86,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,利用了「來」和「愛情」的雙關
